ta-path-to-node=3D"7,1,0" data-index-in-node=3D"0">git commit -m "Your mess=
age"</code></b> (Permanent local snapshot)</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node=
=3D"7,2,0"><b data-path-to-node=3D"7,2,0" data-index-in-node=3D"0"><code da=
ta-path-to-node=3D"7,2,0" data-index-in-node=3D"0">git push</code></b> (Upl=
oads to the remote server)</p></li></ol><h3 data-path-to-node=3D"8">A Quick=
